вҠў source
  yield code вүЎ function add(a, b) { return a + b; }
  yield language вүЎ javascript

вҠў analyze
  given sourceвҶ’code
  given sourceвҶ’language
  yield findings
  вҲҙ Review В«codeВ» written in В«languageВ». List bugs, style issues, and improvements as a JSON array of objects with keys: severity, category, message.
  вҠЁ findings is a valid JSON array

вҠў summary
  given analyzeвҶ’findings
  yield report
